body:
I submitted a Mirror request at TUNA https://github.com/tuna/issues/issues/363

[TUNA](http://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/) is the open source mirror of TsingHua University (China).

@soumith Are the python whls downloaded from pytorch.org redistributable? If so, TUNA members will be able to create a mirror for Pytorch without legal risk.
